{
  "message": "test(conformance): add FP-P2D-040 sort and FP-P2D-041 any/all oracle-backed fixture packets\n\nAdd 18 new conformance fixture packets covering two parity matrices:\n\nFP-P2D-040 \u2014 DataFrame ordering (10 fixtures):\n- sort_index: ascending/descending for int64 and utf8 index types\n  (strict + hardened), plus null-preservation test\n- sort_values: numeric and utf8 columns, ascending/descending with\n  na_position=last (strict + hardened), plus missing-column error case\n\nFP-P2D-041 \u2014 Series any/all (8 fixtures):\n- series_any: all-falsy, all-missing, mixed-truthy, utf8-truthy\n  (strict + hardened)\n- series_all: all-missing, falsy-with-missing, numeric-truthy,\n  utf8-truthy-with-missing (strict + hardened)\n\nAlso adds artifacts/phase2c/FP-P2D-040/ directory with phase2c\noracle capture artifacts for the DataFrame ordering parity matrix.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
